    <detaileddescription>
<para>This specialized set of classes is derived from <ref refid="classOpFunc" kindref="compound">OpFunc</ref>, and is used to handle Process type calls which need to bypass the Queueing system. These include process, reinit, and other intermediate stage process ops. </para>
